text: Welcome to this inviting one-level home located in the sought-after Vedere Terrace neighborhood. This charming property features 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths and is situated on a peaceful street. Enjoy a spacious living area, a convenient kitchen with stainless appliances, and a lovely dining area perfect for gatherings. Hardwood flooring in the living spaces. The generous primary suite is thoughtfully separated from the other bedrooms to ensure privacy. Outside, relax on the large deck with a fenced yard, ideal for enjoying beautiful summer evenings. Even a peek-a-boo view of the farmlands. An attached garage & additional off-street parking offers convenience at your doorstep. Located close to I-5, it offers easy access for commuters.

Discover a unique opportunity in the charming, historic town of La Conner! This property features a spacious 3-car garage with a fully finished second level with 3 bedrooms and 1 bath, perfect for comfortable living or rental income. With rare commercial zoning in this picturesque town, you can envision retail spaces, additional living quarters, or a mixed-use development. Located across from Pioneer Park and just a block from boat launch, waterfront park. Enjoy easy access to La Conners vibrant main street featuring restaurants, galleries, and waterfront boardwalk. The extra-large lot provides ample space for your vision.
Rehab and build in sweat equity, or tear down and start fresh. This home is ready for a new owner. Excellent location. Corner lot, close to schools and amenities.

Nicely maintained single level 3 bedroom 2 bath home on manicured 2.51 acres. This home has spectacular mountain and territorial views in every direction. Custom built home features: fully paved driveway, covered front porch, large deck in the back. Vaulted ceilings with plenty of light coming through skylights and new Anderson windows. New Roof, new carpet, new kitchen tile floors and wood laminate floors in the bedrooms. Fully fenced orchard with mature fruit trees. Multiple sheds, and also a fenced garden area. Plenty of room for RV and boat parking. Cascade trail across the street!

Make your small town home dreams come true w/ this BEAUTIFUL completely remodeled cape cod home! Stay cool in this summers heat w/ the newly installed A/C. Yes this 1901 home has A/C, new plumbing, electrical, appliances, finishes, & professionally landscaped. Enjoy evenings or mornings on either one of the beautiful private patios. Have fun on the finished w/ wood chips play ground that stays (Trampoline included!)! All of your storage needs are covered w/ a convenient shed off the driveway in the back alley for private parking. Enjoy the RV parking for additional space. Mature apple & plum trees are producing fruit for you to enjoy each year! The home has a main floor primary bedroom. Bonus loft space upstairs and 2 additional bedrooms!

Enjoy spectacular sunsets over Langley Bay, Burrows Bay, and the San Juan Islands from this custom-built home. Revel in the elegance of coffered ceilings in the living room, complemented by a stone fireplace & a gourmet kitchen perfect for culinary delights. Retreat to the primary bedroom boasting a luxurious en suite bath and direct deck access. The lower level offers entertainment with a theatre room, a rec room with a kitchenette, and 2 guest bedrooms. Outside, enjoy manicured grounds with low maintenance landscaping & a separate RV garage. Private community beach access & potential moorage for added convenience and leisure. This is more than just a home; it's a sanctuary where every detail is crafted for your utmost comfort & enjoyment.

Newly installed 30-year roof with transferable warranty! NEW vinyl planking floors, paint throughout, sink & faucet in the kitchen. Newer dishwasher and stove. Light and bright, this two-bedroom home lives large with an open concept kitchen, dining room and great room which includes vaulted ceilings, ceiling fan and built in bookshelves in kitchen and dining room. In home washer and dryer make this home complete. Detached one car garage with parking in front of garage and an assigned spot (3 spots total). Covered front & back porch. Relax at the end of the day enjoying the view and sounds of nature emanating from the expansive green space behind the home. Truly a delightful place to call home with yardwork included in your HOA dues.

Updated, move-in ready 1939 charmer in desirable Hillcrest neighborhood. Ideally located on a level lot close to parks, schools, medical, shopping, & dining, easy access to I-5. This adorable bungalow-style home retains original character w/hardwood floors, built-in storage in breakfast room & hall, and beautiful coved ceilings, and has been updated where it counts: Newer furnace & roof, cement-board siding, new windows, tankless water heater, granite counters & stainless appliances in the kitchen, beautifully tiled bathroom. Spacious primary suite with sitting room, multiple closets, private 3/4 bath. Sunroom (possible 3rd bedroom) leads to covered patio, fenced yard, hot tub, new storage shed. Attached garage, low maintenance fenced yard.

Wonderful & beautiful custom designed home in the Skyline. No steps home offers breath-taking 180' panorama west views from the Olympics all the way to Canada! Upon entering the home, one is greeted with a sense of calm & serenity, creating an atmosphere conducive to relaxation. The house features a large office space, wide hallways and 36 solid doors offering easy access throughout. A spacious parking area w/ boat/RV parking plus an insulated oversized 3-car garage. Gorgeous landscaped yard further enhances the appeal of the home, creating a outdoor space to enjoy & unwind. This residence presents an opportunity to own a showcase home in a desirable location. Close to Skyline Marina, Washington Park and San Juan's Is ferry terminal

Welcome to your dream home in Daycreek! This gem is a 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom and offers the perfect blend of comfort and functionality. With vaulted ceilings and a free-standing propane fireplace to keep you warm. Sitting on 6+ acres, with seven covered parking areas, you'll have ample space for all your vehicles and toys. Animal lovers will appreciate the one-stall barn and large fenced area, perfect for horses or other pets. Entertain with ease using the smoker for BBQ fun, relax in the hot tub, or tackle any project in the large shop. Large blueberry bushes and raspberry plants to snack on. So much room a garden could be added! Don't miss this unique opportunity to own a versatile property that meets all your needs.

Ski and surf paradise on Biglake! Rare 100+/- no bank waterfront w/sandy beach! Incredible yard, bulkhead, & newer dock. Automatic sprinklers & drip system keep this place looking great all Summer. Over sized heated 2+car garage is boat deep & ADU above is complete w/kitchen & separate laundry. Inside the main house take in views of snow capped Mt Baker. Completely renovated/built in 2019 including the garage & ADU. Gas furnace, Tankless water heater, & new central AC will keep you comfortable all year! Outdoor covered living w/overhead heaters is a favorite place to watch the Eagles soar. RV parking w/power & dump station! Beach side fire pit provides a front row seat for enjoying the amazing evening views & infamous July 3 firework show!

Escape to this Northwest contemporary cabin nestled on 10 acres of pristine forest on the sunny south end of Fidalgo Island. Enjoy views and the serene verdant forest of Deception Pass State Park forestlands from this secluded property. This charming cabin offers a rare opportunity to live amidst nature's beauty, with over 1, 300 acres of trails and access to Pass Lake on Fidalgo Island just moments away. The property is fully equipped with utilities, including a 4-bedroom septic system, water, cable/internet and telephone making it a turnkey opportunity for those seeking privacy and tranquility. Live comfortably in the cozy cabin while you plan and build your dream home in this idyllic setting.

Lovely level lot in quiet cul-de-sac of Shelter Bay! Build your dream home, here! Power, water & sewer utilities are in the street. Property backs up to a greenbelt, which gives the possibility of allowing a multi-story home to be built. Shelter Bay enjoys wonderful amenities including a community beach, boat launch, sports courts & 3 par golf course. This is leased land

Welcome home to this new townhome in the Skagit Commons community. Completed in 2022, spacious 1, 212 sf home has one bedroom/bath on the main floor with an open kitchen/dining/living room. Upstairs is another bedroom with a very generous walk-in closet. A full bath with washer and dryer also on the second floor. A large bonus room with high ceilings provides lots of extra room for a second living area or work space. Common House has a large kitchen with dining and a living area. Residents of Skagit Commons also have access to a workshop and craft room. Conveniently located close to Anacortes Forest Lands trails, 10 minutes to Deception Pass, and a quick drive to downtown Anacortes. Please make appointments for showings.

Properties like this do not come available often! Beautiful 17.61 Acres of flat, useable land- setup for livestock or horses. Lush fully fenced pastures, round pen, separate paddocks, corral, head gate, loading ramp, & outbuildings for hay storage. 215'x70' Outdoor riding arena. Home offers 3 bedrooms/ 2.5 baths and 1500+ sq/ft of living space. Primary bedroom with full bath. Large kitchen and living room w/wood stove. Sunroom off West side of home and expansive composite deck overlooking pastures. Wired for generator. Roof replaced 2021, Furnace & Water Heater replaced in 2019. 1 bedroom detached cabin with 3/4 bath. Preinspection completed and reflects meticulous maintenance. Truly a peaceful paradise waiting for you to call home!

Brand New Community Bay View in the Burlington Country Club Area. The plan features 1888 sq ft with 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths. Kitchen Island opens to Great Room, dining area. Primary Bedroom with Large 5 piece Bath and walk-in closet upstairs with 3 other Bedrooms. Large back patio and covered front porch. Bay View schools. Close to Skagit Country Club, Edison, Bow, La Conner and Anacortes. Shopping a short distance away. Special Financing options when working with the Preferred Lender. Buyers are able to customize finishes at the Design Center. For GPS use 16850 Peterson Road.

Visit this beautiful, secluded 5.56 acre parcel with circular driveway at the base of Sauk Mountain. Located just 5 minutes East of Concrete. Come explore the hiking/biking trails or just relax by the firepit. This partially cleared property offers a 4 Bedroom Septic system, DOA approved water mitigation certificate, and electricity at the street. Just 1/4 mile from a Skagit River boat launch. Enjoy swimming, fishing, tubing, kayaking, and eagle watching. If your dream is to stay or play. You just found it. This property is located out of the flood plain.

Newer 4-bedroom residence, completed in 2020, with two-car garage. The kitchen boasts elegant granite countertops, maple cabinets, and sleek stainless steel appliances. Its open floor plan showcases hardwood floors throughout. Upstairs, discover a generously sized primary bedroom with a full ensuite bathroom, walk-in closet, and new flooring. Additionally, two more bedrooms upstairs, one with recent flooring updates, and a fourth bedroom downstairs which offer flexible living arrangements. Enjoy the outdoors on the inviting patio area that would be great for a firepit, perfect for cozy autumn evenings. Benefit from RV parking and the efficiency of a tankless water heater. Conveniently located just a short drive to NAS Whidbey and Anacortes.

Discover the perfect blend of comfort and coastal charm in this Skyline neighborhood gem. Nestled on a spacious lot with panoramic Marina & Burrows Bay views, this split-level home offers versatility and serenity. Enjoy two distinct living areas, each adorned with a cozy fireplace. The primary bedroom boasts a relaxing sitting area and a generous walk-in closet. Step out onto the deck from the kitchen and dining area to soak in the stunning vistas. Just a stroll away from Washington Park and conveniently close to the San Juan ferry terminal, Skyline's amenitiesincluding a marina, sports courts, parks, and clubhousespromise a vibrant coastal lifestyle.

Saratoga Stablesa magnificent gated 17+ acre equestrian estate w/panoramic SW views of Saratoga Passage. Exceptional 5, 400+ SF Hamptons-inspired home w/tasteful, high-end restoration including a true chefs kitchen w/SieMatic cabinets & Thermador Professional appliances. 5BR 6BA designer fixtures, zinc & wine barrel wood bar, in-floor radiant heat, wide-planked oak floors, 600 bottle custom wine cellar. Indoor 100 X 200 dressage riding arena & 9 stall barn, 2 grooming stalls, tack room & bath. 6 total tax lots incl fenced pastures & undeveloped 8 acres. Huge garage w/custom cabinets, commercial generator & fully irrigated grounds. Meticulously maintained & spectacularly appointed w/breathtaking views-this is the rarest of opportunities!

REMODELED 3BR, 1.75BA must-see home! Find your new home in this gated community just south of E College Way! Shopping, schools, parks, restaurants, hospital, downtown Mount Vernon are in your backyard! Easy access to I-5. Home includes a covered carport for at least 2 cars. Garage/shed has a NEW circuit panel and electric garage door opener. Large patio in the back with room to garden! NEW roof in 2022, NEW PEX water pipes, NEW Rinnai tankless water heater, NEW Lifeproof brand flooring, NEW Shaker white cabinets, NEW Kohler sinks/faucets, all NEW LG appliances: gas convection stove/air fryer, refrigerator, dishwasher, new HUGE island, and much more! UPDATES ATTACHED. Ask your agent for details! 55+ park

Discover boundless potential with this spacious property boasting stunning water vistas. Embrace the charm of this cottage home, ripe for your imaginative flair. With ample room to renovate or rebuild, the expansive lot offers a picturesque backdrop for your dream abode. Positioned in a prime location, this investment opportunity comes with a freshly painted exterior and a roof in top condition. This home is move in ready! Close to town, right down the road from the ferry, large lot with gardens. You dont want to miss this!!! Seller ficnianing avalible.

Located in Historic La Conner on the coveted hill, this charming home is within walking distance to the LaConner waterfront and the best restaurants, shopping, parks, schools and just about anything you could need and overflowing with local history! The yard is fenced & private with fabulous perennial landscaping. The main level features high ceilings, an open floor plan and a cozy fireplace. This home has 3 bedrooms, 1 3/4 baths and includes a sauna, additional 3/4 bath and a wine cellar in the basement. Out back is a wonderful patio, raised bed & separate studio/office that add to the charm. This property has two parcels, so use your imagination.

Welcome to your new home! This single level home with a view to Mt Baker offers all the stylish and modern upgrades seen in new construction. Walking through the front door youre greeted with luxurious finishes such as quartz countertops, soft-close cabinets, designer lighting, and a floor plan made for easy living and entertaining. Located in the heart of Anacortes, near to highways, grocery stores, and restaurants. This massive 7, 405 sq ft property includes a carport, 2 workshops and a fully fenced backyard. New items are too many to list but include: Electrical, Plumbing, Windows, Drywall, Roof, Laminate Hardwood, Tile, Doors, Cabinets, Countertops, SS Appliances, Insulation, Landscaping and more! No Stone Was Left Unturned Here!

Come build your Anacortes dream home! Awesome gently sloped lot sitting on just shy of half an acre with views out to Fidalgo Bay and beyond. Great location within city limits and one of the last lots left in the Stittwood neighborhood. Just minutes away from not only downtown, Highway 20 access but also the Anacortes Community Forestlands including Whistle Lake just up the road. Lot provides all city utility amenities in the street and is ready to build on! Plus plenty of room to include RV/boat parking. Bring your plans and make it happen.
nearby_schools: Anacortes School District, Northwest Educational Service District 189

text: This charming property offers a serene and peaceful ambiance that is sure to captivate you. With 2 bedrooms and 1 bathroom, this cozy home is ideal for those seeking a recreational retreat in a picturesque setting. Surrounded by the sounds of nature, this property provides the perfect escape from the hustle and bustle of everyday life. Imagine fishing right off your property or enjoying camping adventures with friends, creating lasting memories in this beautiful setting. Looking for a weekend getaway? Look no further, this waterfront gem has the potential to fulfill all your desires.

Cutest rambler in Bakerview West! Sellers have made some nice improvements to the home for you to enjoy! Newer mini-split for heating and cooling, newer roof, newer hot water tank, attic and crawlspace all tidied up and all the appliances stay! Pre-inspected. Primary bdrm w/walk-in closet & continental entry to hall bath. 2nd bdrm features brand new carpet. Tile flooring in kitchen/dining area. The slider opens to a patio and fully fenced back yard. Established landscape, water feature and a garden shed. There is wisteria, cherry and apple trees and even blueberries! Located across the street from the highly acclaimed 40 acre Bakerview Park (off-leash dog area, skate park, play areas) and a block away from the Kulshan Trail access.

Desirable value, style & comfort in this gorgeous upgraded 2013 4 BR in sought after Skagit Highlands! Lovely open great room plan w/spacious 1943 asf, new luxury vinyl/hardwoods, new premium carpet +entire house freshly painted--inside & out! Beautiful chef's island kitchen w/slab granite, abundant cabinets, eating bar, & stainless appliances incl new range & dishwasher; white painted mill work throughout, grand 2 story entry, inviting lg primary suite w/walk-in, tiled shower & dual vanities +an upstairs laundry w/new washer, (both W/D included). Outside finds hardiplank siding, a covered front porch & attractive landscaping w/freshly stained backyard fencing. Wonderful community--7 parks +nature trails & EZ access to all amenities!

Custom built one level home situated on 19.5 acres of rich farmland. This solid built brick home is offering approx. 1761 s/f , open floor plan, 3 lg bedrooms, 2 full baths, living/dining rooms & plenty of storage areas. Spacious 768 s/f attached 2 car garage with massive storage & shop area. A separate location with a driveway, slab, septic system, drilled well & power. Buyer to confirm with county as to possibilities. Enjoy the gorgeous Eastern sunrises, Western sunsets & open pastoral views. There is a variety of black walnut, hart nut, English Walnut, Italian prune & cherry trees.

Fixer, Fixer, smells like money! Bring your toolbox or contractor. 2 bed home in the lovely Cape Horn community, across the street from the Skagit River. Great place to vacation. River access thru Community Park

Step into the Charm of 1900 in this classic 2-story with basement. 1 full acre lot with a 2880 sf shop/garage. This country home on the flats of Skagit Valley is ready for your creativity to make it shine. Spacious rooms throughout the home, high ceilings, large living room, separate dining rm, tv/office room, kitchen w/newer appliances, 2 full bathrooms, 3 large bedrooms and optional rooms up and down for a possible office. Incredible valley and mountain views from every window. Full basement partially finished w/additional 1, 324 sq ft and a roughed in 3/4 bathroom. Nice 40x72 shop with 220 amps, and three 10 foot doors. RV parking on slab with 50amps and pump outs. Fully fenced back yard, large deck needing repair.

Fully renovated in 2020 & move in ready! Covered front patio entry leads to spacious living room w/ vaulted ceilings & large windows for lots of natural light complete w/ cozy gas f/p & slider to private rear patio w/ storage closet & greenbelt backing. Lovely quartz kitchen w/ ample cabinet & counter space, matching appliances & full dining room. Main floor primary suite w/ bay window overlooking the forest & 3/4 bath w/ tile surround. Upstairs find 2 additional generous size bedrooms w/ their own balcony & storage closet & full guest bathroom. Large attached 2 car garage for parking & more storage space. New water heater in 2023, most appliances under 12 months old. New roof 2023. You will not want to miss this stunning condo!

Looking for a cozy 3bed 2bath rambler in an ideal location? With new carpet&LPV flooring, fresh interior paint, newer appliances, roof&gutters cleaned & moss-treated, you may move right in. Four skylights fill this spacious home w/natural light. Storage will not be a problem w/tons of built-ins in the roomy 2-car garage, pantry, kitchen & a large shed boasting an attic & workbench. Fully fenced yard, mature landscaping, a dry stream bed, fruit trees & an herb garden w/fresh topsoil is ready for your green thumb. Minutes to I-5, shopping, dining, medical, schools, parks & gas stations. All appliances stay. No HOA. Pre-inspected. With all major amenities so close, you are still in a peaceful & quiet neighborhood on a cul-de-sac. Welcome home!

Discover the tranquil living of this 55+ community condo designed for comfort and convenience. This single-level unit is bathed in natural light, featuring 2 bedrooms and 1.75 bathrooms across 1130 sq ft of spaciousness. The large kithcen includes an island and ample storage, perfect for culinary enthusiasts. A 2-car garage offers easy parking, while a community clubhouse provides a venue for social gatherings. Residents also benefit from RV parking, catering to diverse lifestyle needs. Enjoy a vibrant community atmosphere with all the comforts at The Cedars 55+ condos.

Picture living at Lake McMurray with the water a block away, in a house that's like new throughout, having a large garden & 24x48 shop. Sound good? We have that very thing that has just come on the market! Spacious living room with great built ins, very nice kitchen with quiet close cabinets & all appliances included, utility area at end of kitchen, primary bedroom is 12x18, bath has large walk-in shower & good-sized double vanity. The garage has space for one car and the remainder is storage. The shop has space for about anything, is insulated and has a high door. Additional 20x10 storage building. Beautifully landscaped yard with large backyard patio area & firepit. Well is 60' with submersible pump. Heat is elec. radiant ceiling panels

Centrally located in Anacortes, this charming Cedar Springs residence, crafted by Strandberg Construction, embodies comfort and livability with the beautiful grounds maintained for you.. Experience the ease of single-level living under high ceilings, abundant natural light, and an open floor plan. Indoors, find tasteful accents, including granite countertops, hardwood floors, and French doors opening to a cozy covered patio overlooking the spacious back green area. Secluded amidst greenery, it offers privacy, along with an attached one-car garage. Exterior maintenance by the HOA ensures immaculate grounds and carefree living for you. Close to shopping, hospital, and community pool.

This craftsman-style home located in the desirable Hillcrest features an open-concept design that connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, creating an inviting atmosphere for both everyday living and entertaining. Enjoy the convenience of having your primary bedroom on the main floor, complete with ensuite bathroom. The kitchen features stainless appliances, granite countertops, and an island which provides additional seating and workspace. Upstairs, you'll find two bedrooms connected with Jack-n-Jill full bath a multipurpose loft area. The fully fenced yard w/patio area is ideal for summer barbecues and gatherings. Use your imagination for the finished storage space above the 2 car garage. Room for RV parking.

Escape to your own serene haven in this stunning custom home set on over 5 acres near Big Lake. Start your day w/prime views of majestic Mt. Baker & bask in the beauty of nature surrounding your retreat. Designed for seamless indoor-outdoor living, an open floor plan creates a perfect setting for hosting gatherings. Unwind in the luxurious primary suite with cozy fireplace & recently updated 5-piece ensuite. Discover additional bedrooms, versatile office/guest spaces, & media room w/wet bar. Recent upgrades include roof, mahogany deck & music studio in the garage. Enjoy the tranquility of this property while still being just a short drive from amenities in Mount Vernon. Embrace the best of both worlds - privacy & convenience await you here.

Located in the heart of Anacortes, this traditional 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home, just a few minutes' drive from downtown and within walking distance of Little Cranberry Lake and Anacortes forest lands famous trails. The main level features an open kitchen, dining room, laundry room, and family room with a cozy fireplace for gatherings. Enjoy partial ocean views while preparing meals.Upstairs has all three bedrooms and views of Cypress, Lopez, and Guemes Islands. The master bathroom has been recently renovated with a stand-up shower and his/hers private sinks.The property includes an attached garage for secure vehicle storage and a new deck in the backyard, perfect for enjoying sunny days.

Well maintained Sedro Woolley home ready for you to move in! This charming split-level 4-bedroom, 2-bath property has been thoughtfully cared for. The roof is just 5 years old, the hot water heater is only 2 years old, and windows replaced 3 years ago and recent new flooring, this home is truly turn-key. The upper level features 2 bedrooms, including a spacious main bedroom, while the lower level offers 2 additional bedrooms, perfect for creating a dedicated home office or guest space. The 2-car garage provides plenty of storage with a newer garage door, and the laundry room is conveniently located downstairs. Come and see this beautiful, move-in-ready home before its gone!

Welcome to your lakefront cottage in the charming McHaven Park neighborhood! This 414 sq ft Park model is ready to make your vacation dreams a reality! A primary suite complete w/ main floor bathroom, plus a loft perfect for guests. Great kitchen space w/ dining area, a cozy living rm, gas fireplace & plenty of storage to keep organized. A covered deck w/ stunning lake views. The perfect spot to relax & unwind after a day of fishing. Located in a quiet neighborhood this is perfect for those seeking a tranquil getaway. A detached tool shed for extra storage. Additional amenities include a bath house w/coin laundry, 1 dock space & easy access to the public boat launch. Don't miss your chance to own a piece of paradise on Lake McMurray.

Welcome to this turnkey rambler in charming Mount Vernon! Instantly feel at home with an inviting open floor plan that flows seamlessly from the kitchen to your covered private back patio. Discover everything you desire: well-sized bedrooms, multiple living areas, and sleek stainless-steel appliances. The fully fenced backyard features a delightful vegetable garden, complemented by a spacious two-car garage and whole-home AC. Nestled on a tranquil tree-lined street, this peaceful neighborhood offers a serene escape from city life while remaining close to schools, shopping, hospitals, and parks. Enjoy nearby lakes, rivers, and hiking trails on your days off. This is home!

Beautifully renovated 2 bed, 2 bath condo nestled in the Skyline Community w/ Parks, Tennis Court & Playground right next door. Walk to your community beach or Clubhouse. Vaulted ceilings capture the natural light & new sliding glass door leads to private deck off living room. Tile floors in main living areas & bathrooms, newer neutral carpet in bedrooms. Curl up with a good book by the gas FP. This condo is lightly lived in & features newer stainless appliances, granite counters, newer cabinetry, fixtures & lighting. Washer & Dryer remain, newer blinds, fresh interior paint 2 years ago. New roof in Spring of 2023. The primary bedroom has a 2nd private deck & lovely primary bath. Enjoy all the community of Skyline has to offer.
